<l>kāmam viṭuvoṉṟō nāṇviṭu naṉṉeñcē </l>
<l>yāṉō poṟēṉiv viraṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my good soul, give up either lust or honour, as for me I can endure neither.</l>
